#. Description of the theme
#, gp-priority: high
msgid "Davis is a teeny-tiny WordPress theme that can be used a starter theme or a really lightweight blog theme. It consists of three PHP files and weighs in at just 36 KB, excluding screenshot.png. It features the aside post format, Block Editor support, featured images, and a responsive design. Demo: https://andersnoren.se/themes/davis/"
msgstr "Davis is a teeny-tiny WordPress theme that can be used a starter theme or a really lightweight blog theme. It consists of three PHP files and weighs in at just 36 KB, excluding screenshot.png. It features the aside post format, Block Editor support, featured images, and a responsive design. Demo: https://andersnoren.se/themes/davis/"

